Protest of Campus Jamiat About Hanged Abdul Qadir Mulla 

Bangladesh Main Assistant Secretary General Jamaat-e-Islami Bangladesh Abdul Qadir Mulla k Bangladesh Supreme Court K faisly par Sazaye Mout k khilaf Aur KMC k Prof. K Islam k Shaayer k Behurmaty aw Huzoor(S.W.A.W) k Shaan main Gustakhi k Khilaf Islami Jamiat Talaba University Campus Peshawar ka Main Road Block Muzahera.Sankro talaba k Shrkat. . .
Prof. Ko terminate krne ka Mutalba.
